    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Before you begin...</strong></p><p>Get all your ingredients and equipment ready</p><p>Skim through these steps, then wash your fruit and veg</p><p>Note: Equipment and pan sizes vary. Make sure you cook food thoroughly (even if it takes you a little longer than 10 min)</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/halloumi-tacos-with-peri-peri-mayo/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>mayo</strong>,<strong> ground smoked paprika</strong>,<strong> dried oregano</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>cider vinegar</strong> to a small bowl</p><p>Add 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give it a good mix up \u2013 this is your <strong>peri peri mayo</strong></p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/halloumi-tacos-with-peri-peri-mayo/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Drain and rinse your<strong> sweetcorn</strong></p><p>Slice your<strong> spring onion[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Cut your <strong>lime[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Cut <strong>half</strong> the<strong> lime[s]</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/halloumi-tacos-with-peri-peri-mayo/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained sweetcorn</strong> and <strong>chopped spring onion</strong> to a bowl</p><p>Add the <strong>juice</strong> of the <strong>halved lime[s]</strong> (save the wedges for later!) and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong>, give it a good mix up \u2013 this is your <strong>sweetcorn salsa</strong></p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/halloumi-tacos-with-peri-peri-mayo/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Cut your<strong> avocado[s]</strong> in half lengthways, around the stone[s]</p><p>Remove the stone[s] using a teaspoon</p><p>Scoop the <strong>avocado</strong> out of the skin[s] using a spoon and slice it finely, lengthways</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/halloumi-tacos-with-peri-peri-mayo/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non stick) over a high heat</p><p>Cut your <strong>halloumi</strong> into 6 slices per person</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>halloumi slices</strong></p><p>Cook for 1-2 min on each side or until golden</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/halloumi-tacos-with-peri-peri-mayo/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> tortillas</strong> to a plate</p><p>Put the plate in the <strong>microwave</strong> and cook for 1-2 min, or until warmed through (alternatively, add the tortillas to a baking tray and put them in the oven for 2-3 min!)</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/halloumi-tacos-with-peri-peri-mayo/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> golden halloumi</strong> to the <strong>warmed tortillas</strong></p><p>Top with the<strong> sweetcorn salsa</strong> and<strong> sliced avocado</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the<strong> peri peri mayo</strong> and serve a<strong> lime wedge</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
